      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is incredibly valid to feel that what you are experiencing is an end, rather than just a setback. Sometimes the goal of therapy isn't to \"fix\" the past, but to help you build a meaningful life *from* where you are right now. If feeling like the old self is gone, perhaps the focus can shift to acknowledging and creating space for the person you are in this moment. Please know that even if your old dreams are gone, you have the power to define what your life means starting today.",
      "source": "target",
